<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>TripCraft | Account Activation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f3f5f7;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #2b2b2b;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }

    .email-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35, #f54927);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 36px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 32px 28px;
    }

    .email-body h2 {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #f54927;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 28px 0;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .email-body p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #fafafa;
      padding: 24px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    a {
      color: #f54927;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 24px;
      background-color: #f54927;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #e33c1f;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to TripCraft üåç</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hey <strong>
          <%= name %>
        </strong>,</p>
      <p>
        Thanks for joining <strong>TripCraft</strong> ‚Äî your gateway to exploring the world!
        To activate your account, please use the following one-time verification code:
      </p>

      <h2>
        <%= otp %>
      </h2>

      <p>
        This code is valid for the next <strong>5 minutes</strong>.
        Enter it on the activation page to complete your registration.
      </p>

      <p>
        Didn‚Äôt sign up for TripCraft? You can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>
        Need help? Reach out to us at
        <a href="mailto:support@tripcraft.com">support@tripcraft.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>¬© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> TripCraft. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>